name: Asuka Langley Souryuu/Shikinami (Evangelion)
description:
Lora model for Asuka from Evangelion. I hope noone will be mad that I made this TwT I'm aware that there already are models of Asuka. I was about to make Mari model, but then I noticed that those existing Asuka models are mostly focused on doing their own thing and there is no normal anime model with focus on outfits like I've been doing.

I've put way more work into this one than I usually do so that it can be used to generate pics in many outfits Asuka had ^_^ I made preview pics for them all too.

All previews were made with weight 0.8. I'll post tags for each outfit in list so that hopefully it's more readable:

  • Sundress - souryuu asuka langley, interface headset, blue choker, yellow dress, red footwear.

  • Jacket over plugsuit - souryuu asuka langley, red jacket, bodysuit under clothes, cat hat, red bodysuit, eyepatch. Additionally hands in pockets helps a lot!

  • Standard plugsuit - souryuu asuka langley, interface headset, red bodysuit.

  • Test plugsuit from Rebuild 2.0 - souryuu asuka langley, test plugsuit, headgear.

  • Bikini - souryuu asuka langley, interface headset, striped bikini.

  • Patched up plugsuit from Rebuild 3.0 - souryuu asuka langley, interface headset, red bodysuit, tape, eyepatch. Increase weight of tape if necessary.

  • New plugsuit from Rebuild 3.0 - souryuu asuka langley, interface headset, multicolored bodysuit, eyepatch. Adding red plugsuit to negatives sumewhat helps.

  • School uniform - souryuu asuka langley, interface headset, suspender skirt, red ribbon, white shirt, school uniform, socks, shoes.

  • White plugsuit - souryuu asuka langley, interface headset, white bodysuit, eyepatch.

  • White plugsuit with rainbows - souryuu asuka langley, interface headset, heterochromia, rainbow order, white bodysuit.
